{"tid":1915224,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【戰術】如何應對警方上門鬼祟拉人","createTime":"2020-03-08T05:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T06:37:36.000Z","uid":158270,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8ed116dc6ee791e81397392ca8cec387d718a7","tid":1915224,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:16:43.000Z","msg":"警方上門拘捕要偷偷摸摸，係因為佢哋想低成本拉人，想遇到/冇阻力就拉到人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">拖延、求援、殺傷敵人</span>：一般來講，人多好辦事，遠親不如近鄰。拖延到二十分鐘唔開門，向外大聲求救話有賊擅闖民居/放SOS求救信號（三短三長三短，用笛吹/打燈）/上tg求街援救就可以召集到人先。<br />\n去到依個關頭，你就只可以靠佢地。而你如果咁啱就係街坊，記住唔好空手去，捉賊帶碌掃把棍都係好合理。<br />\n<br />\n捉到人點處理：<br />\n1.可以犧牲自己做破窗&mdash;&mdash;斬手斬腳再放上網承認責任。<br />\n2.照辦煮碗，令佢無可疑地自殺。<br />\n3.銷毁佢哋嘅身份證明文件，咁佢哋就冇得證明自己唔係賊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法律責任：冇手令下擅闖民居就係犯法，冒警係犯法，非法禁錮係犯法，自衞係合法，以為有賊所以去捉賊係合法。"},{"pid":"a5c982f4e6d4e821a6683f7168523e83ce98c154","tid":1915224,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:18:11.000Z","msg":"支持你表演下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca575d9926ecd4be4d1fc551a9e65a6e7a6eea4","tid":1915224,"uid":118330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:18:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"981ad5fc858f1c27b764391c732d125086510867","tid":1915224,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:21:05.000Z","msg":"咪9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624d5d49d8cfa3f4e1d77db3de97dc89b17c63ef","tid":1915224,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:21:23.000Z","msg":"睇完得啖笑"},{"pid":"fcb60dc6531837380599e1352e0ca5a77c898c0e","tid":1915224,"uid":330582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:22:35.000Z","msg":"睇完笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256fb1f10fa6ffc5437ff92f7f78b7a6a032bc92","tid":1915224,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:30:01.000Z","msg":"做嘅人唔會話自己會做，唔做嘅人都唔會特登話自己唔會做。<br />\n失敗主義要成功，第一步就係提出似樣少少嘅理據先。"},{"pid":"27e39f012976f6514d98631eee0ce753158e0368","tid":1915224,"uid":50972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"on撚9 咁無腦都有"},{"pid":"c53b9492ec8d87d3a7edd5bd35eb40b8e58e2f16","tid":1915224,"uid":167506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:31:55.000Z","msg":"其實上門拉人唔好講到好新鮮咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未有反修例之前都有架啦"},{"pid":"e7d86d78ab06cf726bd65fc74c9cb359fed1c22d","tid":1915224,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c53b9492ec8d87d3a7edd5bd35eb40b8e58e2f16","tid":1915224,"uid":167506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:31:55.000Z","msg":"其實上門拉人唔好講到好新鮮咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未有反修例之前都有架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:45:33.000Z","msg":"我只係提供一個制裁黑警嘅方法。<br />\n無錯上門拉人不嬲都有，但想班警察死係新鮮嘅諗法，想佢哋躝屍趷路係新鮮嘅諗法。"},{"pid":"c68e73a96d28bc50d3d6fc3e68145e0cb528a874","tid":1915224,"uid":59297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:47:16.000Z","msg":"講就易"},{"pid":"2ca53c409870b2f27a1662d0bb028fec09b33312","tid":1915224,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2stC8YY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2stC8YY.jpg&h=9f623ce2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f3226037da806276a09deba05021652a6c39c6f","tid":1915224,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c68e73a96d28bc50d3d6fc3e68145e0cb528a874","tid":1915224,"uid":59297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:47:16.000Z","msg":"講就易"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T05:53:30.000Z",